msgctxt "84_Businessman"
msgid "A second ago I saw a guy stuffed in a barrel filled with concrete."
msgstr "A second ago I saw a guy stuffed in a barrel filled with concrete."

msgctxt "96_Businessman"
msgid "I'm sure it was yakuza. They put him in a car and drove off toward the docks. That's just scary..."
msgstr "I'm sure it was yakuza. They put him in a car and drove off toward the docks. That's just scary..."

msgctxt "108_Saejima"
msgid "(I understand that yakuza gotta do what they gotta do, but it ain't something you see every day. Maybe it'll give me a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"
msgstr "(I understand that yakuza gotta do what they gotta do, but it ain't something you see every day. Maybe it'll give me a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>...)"

